data.description: Don't miss out! Home Sweet Home!  This charming, well maintained, move-in ready, updated home is in a quiet country-like location on a paved road in Belleview. .32 acres just minutes away from Ocala, The Villages, and I-75.  Roof 2021.  Two car garage with third parking space.  60' concrete pad on side of home with 30 amp hookup for RV or boat.  3 bedrooms, 2 baths, luxury vinyl plank flooring in living areas and master bedroom, carpet in bedrooms 2 and 3.  Kitchen has exotic granite counter tops with lifetime sealer & 15 year transferable replacement guarantee, marble backsplash.  New refrigerator.  6" baseboards throughout.  Granite tile shower in master bedroom.  New fans & fixtures.  Double doors from dining room lead to enclosed lanai.  Water softener with rust inhibitor.  Whole house filtration system.   Fenced backyard has a shed with electric.  HVAC 2006.  No HOA.  MUST SEE!
